{"id":588647,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【图说天朝】距离全县脱贫还剩x天/","date":"2018-07-10T09:23:35Z","modified":"2018-07-10T09:23:35Z","title":"【图说天朝】距离全县脱贫还剩X天","content":"<p>【编者按】近日，一张来源不详的“某县脱贫倒计时还剩011天”的图片流传网络，此县级“脱贫攻坚”举措的政治背景来自习近平2017年十九大报告中提出的：</p>\n<blockquote><p>“要动员全党全国全社会力量，坚持精准扶贫、精准脱贫，确保到2020年中国现行标准下农村贫困人口实现脱贫。”</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/img_0119.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-588651\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/img_0119.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a></p>\n<p>中国数字时代曾经报道过所谓“精准扶贫”背后，以政府公权力为推手的“政治大跃进”所制造的诸多问题。</p>\n<blockquote><p><a title=\"【立此存照】精准删帖\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%b2%be%e5%87%86%e5%88%a0%e5%b8%96/\">【立此存照】精准删帖</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"点点寒冰：贵州一老师发微博妄议当地扶贫工作被行政拘留\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/09/%e7%82%b9%e7%82%b9%e5%af%92%e5%86%b0%ef%bc%9a%e8%b4%b5%e5%b7%9e%e4%b8%80%e8%80%81%e5%b8%88%e5%8f%91%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e5%a6%84%e8%ae%ae%e5%bd%93%e5%9c%b0%e6%89%b6%e8%b4%ab%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c%e8%a2%ab/\">点点寒冰：贵州一老师发微博妄议当地扶贫工作被行政拘留</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90%e5%86%8d%e4%b8%80%e7%9c%8b%e3%80%91%e5%86%b0%e8%8a%b1%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%a9%ef%bc%8c%e7%88%b1%e5%9b%bd%e5%ae%a3%e4%bc%a0%e4%b8%8e%e6%89%b6%e8%b4%ab%e9%82%aa%e8%b7%af/\">【再一看】“冰花男孩”，爱国宣传与扶贫邪路</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【立此存照】“婚姻扶贫”：为了小康社会，女性成了“维稳资源”\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%a9%9a%e5%a7%bb%e6%89%b6%e8%b4%ab%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%ba%e4%ba%86%e5%b0%8f%e5%ba%b7%e7%a4%be%e4%bc%9a%ef%bc%8c%e5%a5%b3%e6%80%a7/\">【立此存照】“婚姻扶贫”：为了小康社会，女性成了“维稳资源”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>在网上稍加检索可以发现，“脱贫倒计时”并非个别现象，多地打出宣传条幅，力争在短时间内，实现当地的“脱贫”任务。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1-1P619105435Z0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-588652\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1-1P619105435Z0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"409\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1-1P619105435Z0.jpg 866w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1-1P619105435Z0-300x223.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1-1P619105435Z0-768x571.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9kosp5j21400u0guy.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-588653\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9kosp5j21400u0guy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9kosp5j21400u0guy.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9kosp5j21400u0guy-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9l1holj21400u0n2w.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-588654\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9l1holj21400u0n2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9l1holj21400u0n2w.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/8f5a8315gy1ft3s9l1holj21400u0n2w-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/845431f142f14c09b8b36cba120a83a9.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-588655\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/845431f142f14c09b8b36cba120a83a9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/845431f142f14c09b8b36cba120a83a9.png 549w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/845431f142f14c09b8b36cba120a83